If i invested 1,000,000 into SP500

```{python}

SP500initial_price = 6448.26 
SP500end_price = 6849.72
initial_investment = 1000000

SP500shares = initial_investment / 6448.26

initial = SP500shares * SP500initial_price
end = SP500shares * SP500end_price

SP500_profit = end - initial
SP500_return_pct = (SP500_profit / initial_investment ) *100

print(f"SP500 profit: {SP500_profit}")
print(f"SP500 return_pct : {SP500_return_pct}")
